{"id":14985,"date":"2024-02-08T15:37:23","date_gmt":"2024-02-08T15:37:23","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.geetra.com\/?p=14985"},"modified":"2024-02-17T13:48:54","modified_gmt":"2024-02-17T13:48:54","slug":"how-to-apply-for-fafsa-loans","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/geetracom.local\/how-to-apply-for-fafsa-loans\/","title":{"rendered":"How to Apply for FAFSA Loans &#8211; Step-by-Step Guide"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>If you are looking for steps to apply for the Free Application for Federal Student Aid (FAFSA), this page is for you. The FAFSA allows students in the United States to apply for financial aid to support their education. The application begins with a holistic eligibility check process for approval.<\/p><div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_65 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title \" >Headings On this Page<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/geetracom.local\/how-to-apply-for-fafsa-loans\/#Free_Application_for_Federal_Student_Aid_FAFSA\" title=\"Free Application for Federal Student Aid (FAFSA)\">Free Application for Federal Student Aid (FAFSA)<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/geetracom.local\/how-to-apply-for-fafsa-loans\/#What_is_FAFSA_Loans\" title=\"What is FAFSA Loans?\">What is FAFSA Loans?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/geetracom.local\/how-to-apply-for-fafsa-loans\/#How_to_Apply_for_FAFSA_Loans\" title=\"How to Apply for FAFSA Loans\">How to Apply for FAFSA Loans<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/geetracom.local\/how-to-apply-for-fafsa-loans\/#Deadline_to_Submit_Application\" title=\"Deadline to Submit Application\">Deadline to Submit Application<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/geetracom.local\/how-to-apply-for-fafsa-loans\/#How_to_Check_FAFSA_Application_Status\" title=\"How to Check FAFSA Application Status\">How to Check FAFSA Application Status<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p>First, you must begin by submitting an application from the FAFSA portal.<\/p>\n<p>This page highlights the steps to complete your application to FAFSA for loan approval.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"skip-to-h1\" class=\"text-red\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Free_Application_for_Federal_Student_Aid_FAFSA\"><\/span><strong>Free Application for Federal Student Aid (FAFSA)<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The portal for the application will be opened from 1<sup>st<\/sup> October. Interested students and parents be watchful as early application is the best period for application.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_is_FAFSA_Loans\"><\/span><strong>What is FAFSA Loans?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Federal Student Aid is a loan scheme provided to undergraduate, graduate, and professional students in the United States in the form of grants, loans, work-study, and more to help students pay for college or career school.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Apply_for_FAFSA_Loans\"><\/span>How to Apply for FAFSA Loans<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>To apply,<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>Visit the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.usa.gov\/fafsa\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/www.usa.gov\/fafsa<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Create an account (only for first-time visitors). Sign in instead if you are a returning applicant.<\/li>\n<li>Provide a Username and Password<\/li>\n<li>Fill out and submit your form<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Deadline_to_Submit_Application\"><\/span><strong>Deadline to Submit Application<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The deadline to submit an application is June 30, 2024, for the school year 2023 \u2013 2024<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Check_FAFSA_Application_Status\"><\/span><strong>How to Check FAFSA Application Status<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>To check the FAFSA application status after you have submitted the application, do the following<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>Sign in to the existing <a href=\"https:\/\/studentaid.gov\/fsa-id\/sign-in\/landing\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">account<\/a> with username and password<\/li>\n<li>Hover to application status<\/li>\n<li>Check status.<\/li>\n<li>Other method could via contacting the FAFSA <a href=\"https:\/\/studentaid.gov\/help-center\/contact\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">information center<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The portal for the application will be opened on October 1. Interested students and parents should be watchful, as early application is the best period for application.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":14986,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[42],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/geetracom.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14985"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/geetracom.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/geetracom.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/geetracom.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/geetracom.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=14985"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/geetracom.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14985\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/geetracom.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/14986"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/geetracom.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=14985"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/geetracom.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=14985"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/geetracom.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=14985"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}